  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "000fc05",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "قبعة دافئة تحافظ على دفء رأسك.",
      "sourceEnText": "A warm hat keeps your head warm.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_000fc05.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2795,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:05Z",
      "textHash": "fb26f5f699e4d0bc9b7cbea481738ecec59f7f7989052b215f95ebeac13252d6"
    },
    {
      "key": "001e940",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "لنجب على ثلاثة أسئلة تتعلق بالجبال قبل مباراة العلم.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's answer three mountain questions before the flag game.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_001e940.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5224,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:40:51Z",
      "textHash": "6a6cd26f0bb81b4b81b7d29e5e646bcf9577c41e4acebbe57ab6a81242b9cc5f"
    },
    {
      "key": "003e87c",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_bonus",
      "sourceText": "لقد وجدت وشاحًا دافئًا!",
      "sourceEnText": "You found a warm scarf!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003e87c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:49Z",
      "textHash": "046a9924320cbf14151d9419305d5a9e9e040f029ae42127b44d810f033e096e"
    },
    {
      "key": "003ecb2",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "مونت بلانك هو أعلى جبل في جبال الألب!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mont Blanc is the highest mountain in the Alps!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003ecb2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2769,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:51Z",
      "textHash": "a60d1a16aed9c885ebac438e5c21794569076884a06bae7af1d5616f9b8283ac"
    },
    {
      "key": "00a7e83",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "صحيح! استخدمها للحفاظ على ثباتك.",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct! Use them to stay steady.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_00a7e83.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:20Z",
      "textHash": "6fe2bd350988bd639a6cd04ee79dc1d8e74b39495791f1836d82308bcc9c267d"
    },
    {
      "key": "011dc7e",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "أحب الجبال!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love the mountains!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_011dc7e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1306,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:50Z",
      "textHash": "c3b695be8a597473b9512953a09ffaee4fb5544e0b88e948413c2c17ee2408b7"
    },
    {
      "key": "015bf8a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "أنت الآن جاهز للتسلق!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are now ready to climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_015bf8a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2064,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:59Z",
      "textHash": "a3265485a4c48506397dbdaa6e70221405c4314ec93540dc54425d85b3f1d3cb"
    },
    {
      "key": "018880a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "يبلغ ارتفاع هذه القمة 4807 أمتار.",
      "sourceEnText": "This summit is 4807 meters high.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_018880a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4153,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:26Z",
      "textHash": "fa13f0ef7a37363f8fd89c54dbff963107e5fc71827d41e8171d6d232d26a1b1"
    },
    {
      "key": "01a4b20",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "الزعانف",
      "sourceEnText": "Flippers",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01a4b20.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 940,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:21Z",
      "textHash": "3f329c36fb6becf6fc23914bc4e08753b0569b7dd4af8d40f02f5af00a9b5020"
    },
    {
      "key": "01beb5e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "رأينا الكلب يركض صعوداً إلى الجبل.",
      "sourceEnText": "We saw the dog run up the mountain.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01beb5e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2612,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:52Z",
      "textHash": "af2e37d7f3a95640dba6eab002360f7d0cd2b5d5f31a6760864d0ec2fb2594bb"
    },
    {
      "key": "01e5f66",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "يبدو ذلك النهر الجليدي وكأنه نهر متجمد.",
      "sourceEnText": "That glacier looks like a frozen river.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01e5f66.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 3866,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:57Z",
      "textHash": "04361c6428cf6265a6ea0780152212fdcd2f74ed2c7754319857a4affa4236c4"
    },
    {
      "key": "029a03e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "الشمس ساطعة جداً على الثلج. نحتاج إلى حماية أعيننا.",
      "sourceEnText": "The sun on the snow is very bright. We need eye protection.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029a03e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4624,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:09Z",
      "textHash": "4c486065daa5cfb3ab6d35f8b5e707dcfa602c3926589e9d16f4b35936b8f347"
    },
    {
      "key": "029f39c",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "الآن يمكننا الخروج من المعسكر الأساسي وبدء المغامرة!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now we can exit the base camp and start the adventure!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029f39c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4937,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:58Z",
      "textHash": "1d5a0f7fd47ad7839c45ce4dfe50e5a0b151ef8bb6607766d8b44353aa7eb24a"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a2ea9",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "يعكس الثلج والجليد ضوء الشمس الساطع.",
      "sourceEnText": "Snow and ice reflect bright sunlight.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a2ea9.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3213,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:15Z",
      "textHash": "dcba0daa9903ab75ae03dfd8ff6d399ac7aec4d1001eadf5b836a23f85eac754"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a3874",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "لا، سأبقى هنا",
      "sourceEnText": "No, I stay here",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a3874.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1515,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:45Z",
      "textHash": "d23d32539e493ccaa2b21623a3f3991511c8f3eb2d6c00020c344774b8c07324"
    },
    {
      "key": "02c9805",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_3_done",
      "sourceText": "افتح الصندوق لتحصل على المرابط!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get crampons!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02c9805.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3082,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:23Z",
      "textHash": "f0cd59041f74a8f65a3178e1dcaa99a49c59fdfd6e37e5bac71227d6ef1f847b"
    },
    {
      "key": "030fa1c",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "لقد نجحت! نحن الآن على قمة مونت بلانك.",
      "sourceEnText": "You made it! We are at the top of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_030fa1c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3683,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:25Z",
      "textHash": "7df69ed32f9b9130fa6fbaac62997879ee0f6a8c074c7383a3a23a2f31c8adb9"
    },
    {
      "key": "035e68a",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "المعسكر الأساسي 4",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 4",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_035e68a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2612,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:44Z",
      "textHash": "39d8b367667ae90804c3d62905af33e6152a0ae3ec46fb0f080d574c9cdcd938"
    },
    {
      "key": "0371d31",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "التسلق برفقة مرشد أكثر أماناً.",
      "sourceEnText": "Climbing with a guide is safer.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0371d31.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2717,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:59Z",
      "textHash": "aa0d8e07995d1879f6e3fd3df807a87a8e54651b1d0c9a672ae7d8d4d2d539df"
    },
    {
      "key": "038d1bc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_rope",
      "sourceText": "يساعد الحبل المتسلقين على البقاء آمنين على الجليد والصخور.",
      "sourceEnText": "The rope helps climbers stay safe on ice and rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_038d1bc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5277,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:24Z",
      "textHash": "913d6d817cddb79f1b1a1297fbd18599c60eed221fd8b249af9d85bc54fa5cf1"
    },
    {
      "key": "03db010",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_swiss",
      "sourceText": "تقع سويسرا شمال مونت بلانك.",
      "sourceEnText": "Switzerland is north of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03db010.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2247,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:40:53Z",
      "textHash": "770f7fc1aacb3e9f91115c6c1463d1e8e47e86b523af5e1f23a4a3e78bb254ab"
    },
    {
      "key": "03dd802",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "أنت تفتقد المعطف!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the coat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03dd802.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1724,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:00Z",
      "textHash": "c6b7f5f100f01a066eba32f6512461e281c0a720d2bc8a13e907363daeb4e316"
    },
    {
      "key": "045409f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "قبل الذهاب، ستحتاج إلى حقيبة ظهر.",
      "sourceEnText": "Before going, you need a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_045409f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3396,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:54Z",
      "textHash": "77ff13e4771485c9ca8d3fa7e1f1ec681f6f9d95c64e90f186e4ce9a238ea053"
    },
    {
      "key": "046eb33",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "عد عندما تنتهي من المهمة.",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back when you finish the task.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_046eb33.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:50Z",
      "textHash": "5b7f6efeb4659fcf0ba8b51639dcf5e8c17bedf2538de7a0ec6a7b22ee3a4581"
    },
    {
      "key": "04bbada",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "أتمنى أن أرى حيوان المرموط!",
      "sourceEnText": "I hope to see a marmot!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04bbada.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2377,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:52Z",
      "textHash": "f1a939cdd48ee975a1b3dcda55b971cfe8d93ddbd97247fcb80e33db6ad21d29"
    },
    {
      "key": "04c1c1f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "أرى أن لديك حقيبة الظهر. يمكنك الذهاب الآن!",
      "sourceEnText": "I see you have the backpack. Now you can go!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04c1c1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4336,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:48Z",
      "textHash": "d0da2eca399eefbdc831cecccd9f3e14112d8a5140588e7151570160a8de7c0d"
    },
    {
      "key": "050fe70",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_italy",
      "sourceText": "تقع إيطاليا شرق جبل مونت بلانك.",
      "sourceEnText": "To the East of Mont Blanc there is Italy.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_050fe70.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2769,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:39Z",
      "textHash": "7cefbfb813074504ac41e71e11c027fbff2fafc6be2dfa00f5dec29f439033aa"
    },
    {
      "key": "0557ef5",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "يمكن أن تتغير الرياح بسرعة.",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind can change fast.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0557ef5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2560,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:55Z",
      "textHash": "7a27a99427fe7825d6de8cae2c835253bc8b4ff2177ba83fce148be42210ad24"
    },
    {
      "key": "056ec2b",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base1",
      "sourceText": "يفتح! يحتوي على بعض المعدات.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains some equipment.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_056ec2b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2560,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:03Z",
      "textHash": "1c83f371cd446f9bdd1883181722716b2e9ee7ee1e0d846294133a5e7f77f848"
    },
    {
      "key": "058bb65",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "المعسكر الأساسي 3",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 3",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_058bb65.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1829,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:44Z",
      "textHash": "4a0228edf9d8c1e8bccd30b449c4cfc6d9f16beb150d481ad035ca6fa4b4ecca"
    },
    {
      "key": "0590129",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "لا تنسَ إحضار ملابس دافئة!",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't forget to bring warm clothes!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0590129.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:53Z",
      "textHash": "36c3cd08366b208aeeeeaa40afdb648126ff51ccef5b1b14f9a33df33b809804"
    },
    {
      "key": "059d744",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "كما أنه مفيد عندما تكون الرياح باردة.",
      "sourceEnText": "It also helps when the wind is cold.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_059d744.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:06Z",
      "textHash": "5e6880229f903b15e8a695a84451a19ac1cb7ae381e08dbf1528dad0e24b90b8"
    },
    {
      "key": "05cabb5",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "ابحث عنه في كل مكان!",
      "sourceEnText": "Look around for it!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05cabb5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2064,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:55Z",
      "textHash": "3d9d05c9f23c18a89efc6600aec3a00a7f7713c9f5173c4b79864cc2037d7054"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e3658",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "المعسكر الأساسي 2",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 2",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e3658.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1541,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:43Z",
      "textHash": "b5b5dee2f5bd6f9c4fd4e9d43a63bc82e36fec19c2b4523894c4b1b45a09a6cd"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e80cb",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "يمكن لهذه الحقيبة حمل الطعام والماء والخريطة.",
      "sourceEnText": "This backpack can carry food, water, and a map.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e80cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4467,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:57Z",
      "textHash": "b55aa038fe9e15b6599506e6f5e613e8632e11cf17c6a82868d4c0a30575141e"
    },
    {
      "key": "0650acc",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "تفضلوا باستكشاف مونت بلانك وابحثوا عن معداتنا.",
      "sourceEnText": "Please explore Mont Blanc and find our gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0650acc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3500,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:53Z",
      "textHash": "df2db432ec21272763690125440bf2a9727ef9dd556427755ea6a51f4a4a45a3"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b15bb",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "لديك معدات الجليد. دفعة أخيرة نحو القمة!",
      "sourceEnText": "You have the ice gear. One last push to the top!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b15bb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4284,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:16Z",
      "textHash": "b1654e3be625bdc5fd64366e718ff72d46337cc528c38d206b156e9b54930510"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b3363",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "أنت تفتقد القفازات!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the gloves!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b3363.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1933,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:08Z",
      "textHash": "cb58654967c099b35bc6e7e689f49dc6748ef67d20c08c7ce6a6f9f58bfb6aec"
    },
    {
      "key": "06d9f34",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "للمشي على جليد الأنهار الجليدية، نحتاج إلى معدات خاصة.",
      "sourceEnText": "To walk on glacier ice, we need special gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06d9f34.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4937,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:18Z",
      "textHash": "23a5a23ab935d5c26126fcd231c840ad0e5cedcf59b6a907a1b104c2279c3fe2"
    },
    {
      "key": "06f9a2a",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "في أي سلسلة جبال يقع جبل مونت بلانك؟",
      "sourceEnText": "What mountain range is Mont Blanc in?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06f9a2a.mp3",
