    },
    {
      "key": "end_1",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "رائع! لقد وصلت إلى قمة مونت بلانك. يبلغ ارتفاعها 4807 أمتار!",
      "sourceEnText": "Amazing! You reached the top of Mont Blanc. It is 4807 meters high!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_1.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 7549,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:45Z",
      "textHash": "b157c7a4e48518811dbf2f5a88ee62064756f3f6203eb6b135e0b75b88d867d7"
    },
    {
      "key": "end_2",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "جبال الألب مليئة بالجبال الشاهقة والجميلة.",
      "sourceEnText": "The Alps are full of tall, beautiful mountains.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3396,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:25:46Z",
      "textHash": "667d76aefa9beca41eae8b76a81272fbfa9065d3d8449f5d2d9e2279b2f5db83"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_chest",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base2",
      "sourceText": "يفتح! يوجد بداخله نظارات شمسية.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It has sunglasses inside.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_chest.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3814,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:12Z",
      "textHash": "3031d336311b4c26361d78943317fbaa4affb14e0f0e902c4d8c6f963e3d49b6"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_help",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "إذا علقت في مكان ما، يمكن لرجل الثلج أن يساعدك!",
      "sourceEnText": "If you get stuck, the snowman can help!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_help.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4023,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:07Z",
      "textHash": "5bfb11a44684740233365427524143c93d1efe688fea285bfd9bad6d2774473f"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_2",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "أنام ​​طوال فصل الشتاء تحت الثلج. هذا ما يُسمى بالسبات الشتوي!",
      "sourceEnText": "I sleep all winter under the snow. This is called hibernation!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5355,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:46Z",
      "textHash": "8265a7e511c6d7bc1a263729a03dd07dff653851ba1351b85d9c86e8ed15d903"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_3",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "أحب تناول زهور وأعشاب جبال الألب. يا له من طعم لذيذ!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love eating alpine flowers and grass. Yum!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_3.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "haytham",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5277,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:26:47Z",
      "textHash": "b3bfd043009dd5ce2ab8ad0f89bd10394433c5071c0c131cd3005c71e511c395"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_4",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "لا تهتموا بي، أنا فقط أستمتع بحمام شمس على هذه الصخرة الدافئة.",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't mind me, I'm just sunbathing on this warm rock.",
